3	//
4	// WHY THIS MATTERS MORE THAN ANOTHER REGEX:
5	//   Every finding we have ever made is, at bottom, an INTERPRETATION: does this text satisfy this obligation. A
6	//   partner can argue with an interpretation. Nobody can argue with a public register.
