8	//   Under the Data Protection (Charges and Information) Regulations 2018, made under s.137 DPA 2018, a controller
9	//   that processes personal data must PAY A FEE AND BE ON THE ICO REGISTER. Failure is enforceable by the ICO and
10	//   carries a fixed monetary penalty of up to GBP 4,350 (Tier 3 fee x 150%). A law firm with a contact form, a
11	//   client portal and analytics cookies is unquestionably a controller.
